title: American Horror Story Season 8 Hidden Actor, Michael Langdon Returns, and Supreme Theories
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: I think it will center on Michael Langdon.  He's the Antichrist.  It will be kinda like "The Omen" vs. "Coven" perhaps.  That would be AMAZING!❤️👍🥂🙌😊🎈

I have an theory. Since Lady Gaga played Scathage in the reenactment and the OG Supreme IS unknown, maybe Sarah Paulson plays Scathage and since she's a powerful witch, she could most likely bring back all the witches that died, since Ryan asked ALL the witches back.
I want Lana del Rey to be in this season. She would be the perfect og supreme

Here's my theory: the first 5 episodes will be with totally new characters... (Evan as a hairstylist and Sarah with dental apps) and we'll see the real crossover only after episode 5, as Ryan said that a BIG thing happens on this episode. Kind of what happened in Roanoke with the twist.
I want misty to come back 😩😭
